snippet.title: Hand of Fate 2 gameplay - fighting The Empress
snippet.description:
Our uncut demo of Hand of Fate 2 from PAX West 2016. Note that we were using an Xbox controller, which is why the button prompts show up as controller buttons, but the game was running on a PC.

Check out http://www.pcgamer.com for more coverage from PAX West 2016!
